                     <interp inst="t17921031-61-off357" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17921031-61-cd358" type="crimeDate">28th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17921031-61-off357 t17921031-61-cd358"></join>, one cotton frock, value 2 s. one cotton and linen apron, value 21 d. one cotton shirt, value 3 s. and one pinnafore, value 2 d.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17921031-61-victim620" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Matthews
                  <interp inst="t17921031-61-victim620" type="surname" value="Matthews"></interp>
